data.description: ASSUMABLE MORTGAGE with a 2.875% INTEREST RATE available! Check out this beautiful turn-key home that was recently completed in 2020! Located in the highly desired gated community of Los Lagos.  The community features private lakes with launch ramp access for electric boats, a clubhouse with a full kitchen and meeting room, pool, spa, library, pickle ball court, tennis court, a fitness center, access to Los Lagos Golf Club and so much more. The 2,025 single-story square foot home features an open living area, 4 spacious bedrooms and 3 full baths. The master suite offers a well-sized walk-in closet, dedicated mini-split air conditioning unit, dual vanities, spa tub and walk in shower. Kitchen features include beautiful custom wood soft close cabinetry, granite countertops, tiled backsplash, full pantry, stainless steel appliances and kitchen island with seating area. Other amenities include high ceilings throughout, water softener, reverse osmosis water system, ceiling fans and recessed lighting throughout, custom wrought iron dual entry doors and large welcoming foyer. Between the living area and garage is a large utility room with washer and dryer, custom cabinets and granite counter tops. The attached 36  deep garage with epoxy floors has plenty of room for vehicles and toys. The large private backyard offers a covered patio, plenty of room for a pool, outdoor kitchen and so much more. Just minutes away from the Colorado River, Lake Mohave, Laughlin Nevada and off-roading trails. This stunning home is a great value! Motivated Seller!
